      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in showroom condition. From the flawless finish of the exterior to the pristine, smoke-free cabin, every detail has been meticulously preserved. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision of a factory-new model, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our uncompromising criteria. For the enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering stands as a benchmark in its class.",
      "price": 46500.0,
