    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is, for all intents and purposes, indistinguishable from the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a flawless deep obsidian metallic paint protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is free of even the slightest swirl marks or rock chips. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent, featuring premium hand-stitched leather upholstery that shows no signs of wear, creasing, or fading. Every electronic component, from the panoramic sunroof to the advanced driver-assistance systems, functions with surgical precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and maintained exclusively by factory-certified technicians with a complete, documented service history provided. This isn't just a pre-owned vehicle; it is a meticulously preserved specimen for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
