      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six powerplant with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The high-revving 3.2L unit is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering linear power through a factory limited-slip differential. This example is mechanically pristine; the critical rear subframe reinforcement has been professionally addressed, and the rod bearing service is documented and current. The suspension geometry remains true with zero bushing deflection, and the chassis exhibits absolute torsional rigidity. Every component, from the high-pressure fuel rail to the cooling system's expansion tank, reflects a preserved factory state, making this a turn-key acquisition for the discerning purist.",
